{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Algorithms run nearly every part of your life.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e4a34b64b9c90703f5c5f8a43ea4d58db1a283e04cc285bdf61b8c395c79d16e",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Your power grid. Your D N A test. The chips in your phone.",
      "checksum": "sha256:436616f37c2db01dfcc35b8d63a877721b38ddffb4db1da6ae038972a03ce0cd",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Drug discovery, navigation, logistics. Most of them were invented slowly.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83e30be35f106ecdf0820b0a937e7c823fa2550a81e1b13acb4264b19d105dcc",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "By humans. Over decades. Google DeepMind built an AI that does it differently.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5c4865c29d781b08524153e425fb57788a778c3c192b1144f403d51f25ef0bbf",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 31
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "It's called Alpha-Evolve. It's not a chatbot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0d929cd9ee2a025068b6eb13e35b33bfdcda87112140ccb6feab96f990791ce",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "It writes code, tests its own code, and only keeps what works.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4ab3935f328045181f9409f61df9ba0c1a15ad3bd77374b176ae82e4e5093312",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 51
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Like evolution, but for algorithms. In one year, it's quietly improved more than a dozen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e888ca738672a2e52566087c621ecc251837939bb9fdcb50f4d2c0b9b45ab166",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 63
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Here's how good it is. For fifty-three years, the fastest known way to multiply two matrices used forty-nine multiplications.",
      "checksum": "sha256:79c837d617bb7748781ccf2df86fca545479bb2537f54447d1eedfd94cc1cd34",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 7.662585034013605,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 78
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "The record stood since nineteen sixty-nine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fa10e6a4f7d3f155250c3b6fef1174f4599f873b0a5792274e4ae4036a303abe",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 97
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Alpha-Evolve found a way in forty-seven.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8d39dc8f6de09171fc0d35846e2d268d92c9d9479b963d09b5501369ea8d5a04",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 103
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "A tiny number. A huge deal. That single optimization runs inside every AI training cluster on the planet, every single day.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5903797f1638cd1333fdc4e96b38a6033426bc321be3635e9dfeed441ea67874",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 7.894784580498866,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 109
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The power grid is the biggest machine humans ever built.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d892c613acc19195aa0398b11a59ad925eb7e328bd260d7c02dd6bd9b420da80",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "It runs on a math problem called the A C Optimal Power Flow benchmark.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b1e3c9654bf9cee49e5ed1f51ce0bfa25474494c5d06aa4a685b610e7bbb004a",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Human-built solvers found workable answers fourteen percent of the time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3822419982b4ffbd98a721dad22551b550e80e30917c04de134a04508844f70d",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 154
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Alpha-Evolve's solver finds them eighty-eight percent of the time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c7ae175f141b688035f862c80db9417686e76e9b9434f9d3226a46863f3985de",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 164
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "That's the lights staying on. Now medicine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dc5c6fb7ebd509b87bdd7163148b00da992f73df8c69718404b256ba3a577bf3",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 173
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "PacBio runs D N A sequencing in hospitals.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1dc2be3f91b90a000e08586cf11512421999f283565202fb9f7fb9075cf3716b",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Alpha-Evolve rewrote a key piece of their pipeline.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6b65d3d2c88e368cf05dc5b939db2df95ea7d15ced0424767b871367c881d3fc",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 188
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Sequencing errors dropped thirty percent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:de89883ee6c6bee0f285b955e20b7d1113464553a87b024b748a7932fc1020ff",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 196
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Drug-discovery models at Shroh-dinger now train roughly four times faster.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6de2cacc0fff8353269d8ba258d7711a91d8dde0f82837eb340e41b3d4033e06",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 201
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Cheaper, safer experiments. New drugs reach human trials sooner.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3b335f3af1d36f6dfed87da48f915d22f3a50f456ae4b1615a04250a7001444f",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 211
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "That is real-world impact. And here's the part that should make you stop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:282be57a3e1a893d946810c08b649d928449aab00040eb389decfc2784af12cf",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 220
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Google's chief scientist Jeff Dean puts it like this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:79ed93b8235981162228fae803718404e67abe19f06c0fd8b18c6de631958226",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 233
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "T P U brains helping design next-gen T P U bodies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:27ad4ea54dbef048d72cf9c7254ded20b9d4eec57f0c631d4de4f3288b36e701",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 242
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Translation. The AI that runs on Google's chips is now writing the circuits for the next chips.",
      "checksum": "sha256:655075e4ff1460d20c11baa50e517fbf75e9ca45370703882dfea2b056a98d3c",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 253
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "AI designing the silicon that runs AI. Compound interest, in hardware.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0ad7bd6725b48744732af924ff5fd1b84d36007617cf1af29e4256b7d827900f",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 270
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Fair question. How do you trust an AI with drug discovery and power grids?",
      "checksum": "sha256:cb91968ae972e36e21ba0da6df3f1310bdc7f7eecf4740af7d7012685b1bd519",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 281
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Here's the loop. Alpha-Evolve writes a candidate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dd098bdbe075873a9a804867b04e8455e77d3d116c4670c43a4e2bc333a5f67c",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 295
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "An automated test scores it on real data.",
      "checksum": "sha256:920927d3064d8eb8010b5a6809e9be76e8f6e9c3f7f156e4b3ba1a60aed506cc",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 302
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Only solutions that pass survive. Propose.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e78b16ef2c01c853f2af7dad69b4d35fb2573bd7077289ceda353a419ceb53af",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 310
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Test. Keep. No vibes. No hallucinations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:227a0d3d6e73a99f4dc3f5ec244b859cee8af990a216cc1bb7a2812a93cfe8e8",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 316
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "The verifier is the reason it ships. And it's not just Google's lab.",
      "checksum": "sha256:078b52e6a2e00db420a5b8cb627ad608de5c2d5cc5709b42667d381f284b15ef",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 322
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Klarna's transformer training, two times faster.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cb09ce91e25107268b3f6d0642d6a44f16dcec003eb97a6deceb4ca2440ae1aa",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 335
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "FM Logistic's routing, ten point four percent more efficient.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d6b026cac46303d951ed04b75d5c3a066f3722ee5f96b85e68d519cd834e65e",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 341
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Fifteen thousand kilometers a year saved. W P P's ad targeting, ten percent sharper.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8349900d0b545cd42b76b560cb4dd9088244ee60ecddbb6fa3d8dfab83bea16d",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 350
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Six outside partners. Same story. The receipts hold up.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b8e3b0b8900633cd19f807ceb3303b42c78e93af4dba797d327ff5894faaf3b1",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 364
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "So this is the shift the headlines missed. AI is not just chatbots anymore.",
      "checksum": "sha256:33ef75ba9d395764235ef04f6b337175051bcf0aee161f7a95aca011c9bc54df",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 373
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "It's writing the algorithms that run your life.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9ba1b23213d34b140b8b6c5ee28cb3c9b61c8ec82f318a3e5e3f8dcfa3f7de63",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 387
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Quietly. Carefully. With math behind every line.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9da196eb5dededc4758cb8a82f3be7cde033315a31418fc8f3c98514073e2dae",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 395
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "If AI could redesign one part of your daily life, what would you trust it to touch first?",
      "checksum": "sha256:76f4556c7be33f43cd57c5bf9a2af08f0ffed343ca0754c706d3976900d546a7",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 402
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Tell me in the comments. And if you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1163e3e9377c4a010db466da3efaf1f1995845a90cb8d50b5d33038f1958a0ba",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 5.712108843537415,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 420
    }
  ]
}